    <p class="price-note">$120 commercial diagnostic, waived with repair. No emergency surcharge. Bar dispatch combo: glass washer plus under-bar ice machine plus undercounter dishwasher all serviceable on the same visit.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-gray">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <p class="section-number">06 · Brands we service</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Five glass washer platforms cover the LA bar segment.</h2>

    <p><strong>Hoshizaki</strong> (Japanese, separate from their ice machine line): HG-100. Premium quality, common in hospitality and craft bars. Hoshizaki America also acquired the Jackson commercial dishwasher line, see <a href="/brands/jackson-dishwasher-repair/">Jackson commercial dishwasher repair</a>.</p>

    <p><strong>CMA</strong> (Cleveland-based): Glass Mizer line. Common in hotel bars and restaurants. See <a href="/brands/cma-dishmachines-repair/">CMA commercial dish machine repair</a>.</p>

    <p><strong>Champion</strong> (Ali Group): CG-2. Mid-premium, common in chain operations. See <a href="/brands/champion-dishwasher-repair/">Champion commercial dishwasher repair</a>.</p>

    <p><strong>Lamb LM and Moyer Diebel</strong>: legacy bar installs, parts available through manufacturer distribution networks.</p>

    <p>For full undercounter dishwasher scope (not glass-specific), see <a href="/brands/hobart-dishwasher-repair/">Hobart commercial dishwasher repair</a> and <a href="/brands/meiko-dishwasher-repair/">Meiko commercial dishwasher repair</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <p class="section-number">07 · Why operators call us</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Eight reasons.</h2>

    <ul class="why-list">
      <li><strong>Bar service hour awareness.</strong> Friday and Saturday evenings are our highest dispatch volume. We work around your busiest hours.</li>
      <li><strong>Bar dispatch combo.</strong> Glass washer plus under-bar ice machine plus undercounter dishwasher all on the same visit.</li>
      <li><strong>Jet cleaning expertise.</strong> Glass washer jets are smaller than dishwasher jets. Bar residue (sugar, citrus, foam protein) clogs them in patterns we know by brand.</li>
      <li><strong>Spinning wash arm rebalance.</strong> After bearing or jet repair, the arm needs balance verification. Most appliance shops skip this and the arm fails again in 6 months.</li>
      <li><strong>BHGS #A49573 plus EPA 608 Universal #1346255700410.</strong> Verifiable.</li>
      <li><strong>24/7 phone answering, no emergency surcharge.</strong></li>
      <li><strong>Same-day across LA, OC, Ventura.</strong></li>
      <li><strong>Common parts on the van.</strong> Detergent dispensers, drain pumps, door switches, water inlet valves for Hoshizaki HG, CMA Glass Mizer, Champion CG-2.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Sister sub-services: <a href="/commercial/dishwasher-repair/rack-conveyor-dishwasher-repair/">rack conveyor</a>, <a href="/commercial/dishwasher-repair/flight-type-dishwasher-repair/">flight type</a>, <a href="/commercial/dishwasher-repair/undercounter-dishwasher-repair/">undercounter</a>. Parent: <a href="/commercial/dishwasher-repair/">commercial dishwasher repair</a>. Credentials: <a href="/credentials/licensed/">BHGS license</a>, <a href="/credentials/epa-certified/">EPA 608</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-gray">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <p class="section-number">08 · FAQ</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Glass washer repair, common questions.</h2>

    <div class="faq-list">
